    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 75-67-121, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE A LICENSEE UNDER THE SMALL LOAN REGULATORY LAW TO CHARGE A FEE FOR THE PURCHASE OF NONFILING OR NONRECORDING INSURANCE IN LIEU OF THE ACTUAL COST OF RECORDING AN INSTRUMENT EXECUTED AS SECURITY FOR A LOAN; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
